ed="T" n="0870a05"/><persName key="A013605">釋從審</persName>，不詳氏族，幼入<placeName key="PL000000010764"><placeName>江都</placeName><placeName>禪智寺</placeName></placeName>，捨家<lb
ed="T" n="0870a06"/>誦經數萬餘言。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010764">其寺</ref>即<persName key="A004413">隋煬帝</persName>之故宮也。<date key="j20366752037029" notAfter-iso="+0865-02-03" notBefore-iso="+0864-02-15"><name>咸<lb
ed="T" n="0870a07"/>通</name>五年</date>，受具戒於<placeName key="PL000000055666"><placeName>燕臺</placeName><placeName>奉福寺</placeName></placeName>。律席經筵，遍<lb
ed="T" n="0870a08"/>知<ptr type="glossary" target="#g106"/>甞染。後併三衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1386"/>成五納<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1322"/>，諸名山勝概，無<lb
ed="T" n="0870a09"/>不遊覽。末歸<placeName key="PL000000010783">淮甸</placeName>，推為僧首。五六年間，一<lb
ed="T" n="0870a10"/>皆嚴肅。然恒誦《淨名經》<ptr target="#n1177"/>，未愆日計。以<date key="j20557392055739" when-iso="+0916-04-27"><name>貞明</name><lb
ed="T" n="0870a11"/>二年三月十八</date>日構疾，迨<date key="j20557402055740" when-iso="+0916-04-28">十九日</date>禺中<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1731"/>微<lb
ed="T" n="0870a12"/>息而終，顏貌如常。茶毘，獲舍利三十粒，堅<lb
ed="T" n="0870a13"/>明通鍛無耗。疊石為墳，<placeName key="PL000000055397">筠源</placeName>沙門<persName key="A013607">靈護</persName>述<lb
ed="T" n="0870a14"/>墳銘云。</p>
